Product Description

High-Speed Micro HDMI to HDMI Cable

UGREEN Micro HDMI male to HDMI male cable delivers both high-definition video and digital audio from digital devices to your home theater. It offers an ideal way to connect digital devices with Micro HDMI (HDMI Type D) ports to HDTV or Projector with full-size HDMI (HDMI Type A) ports.

Note: Micro HDMI port is different from mini HDMI or Micro USB, please check your device's port before purchase.

10ft can only support 1080P

High-Quality Picture and Sound

Support Max 4K 60Hz, 1440p, 1080p, 1080i, 720p, 480p and 480i Resolution

Support 3D, Ethernet Channel and Audio Return Channel

Support True HD Dolby 7.1 and DTS-HD Master Audio

Read more
Read more

Widely Compatibility

Suitable for action camera, HD camcorder, digital cameras, media-center, HDTV devices, projector, monitors, DVR, Blu-ray-Player, Home Theater Systems and more.

Compatible for GoPro Hero 7 Black, Hero 6 Black, GoPro Hero (2018), Hero 5 Black, Hero 4 Black Silver, GoPro Hero 3 Silver White, Hero 3 Black Edition, HERO3+ Black and Silver Editions.

Compatible for Raspberry Pi 4

Compatible for Sony a5000 handycam, Sony A6000 camera A6300 A6400 A6500, Sony A73 A7S, Nikon b500, Canon EOS M50.

Compatible for Lenovo IdeaPad Miix 300 10" Tablet, Ideatab Miix 700, Lenovo Miix 2 (10-inch) Tablet, MIIX 3-1030, Miix 2 11, Miix 710, Ideatab Miix S6000, IdeaTab S6000 Tablet, IdeaTab Lynx K3011, Lenovo ThinkPad 10 ThinkPad 8.

Compatible for lenovo yoga 2 Pro, Yoga 3 Pro ULTRABOOK, Lenovo Yoga 700, Yoga 710, Lenovo 710s, Lenovo N20P Chromebook, ASUS ZenBook UX305UA, UX430UQ, Transformer Mini T102HA laptop.

Gold-Plated Connectors

This Micro HDMI to HDMI cable features gold-plated connectors that resist corrosion for signal purity.

Important Notes

This is Micro HDMI to HDMI, NOT Micro USB to HDMI. So it does not work with Samsung Galaxy S3 S4 S5 S7 or Kindle tablet without Micro HDMI Port.

This micro hdmi cord cannot fit for GoPro Hero7 Silver & White (Without Micro HDMI Port).

      Size:3FT

      Micro HDMI to HDMI cable and its uses
      Micro HDMI to HDMI cable delivers both high-definition video and digital audio from digital devices to your home theater.It offers an ideal way to connect digital devices with Micro HDMI (HDMI D) ports to HDTVs or Projectors with full-size HDMI (HDMI A) ports. Please note that micro HDMI ports are different than mini HDMI-check your device's port
      Quality Picture and Sound
      -Supports 3D, Ethernet and Audio Return
      -Guaranteed 1440p, 1080p, 1080i, 720p, 480p, and 480i Resolutions
      -HDCP Compliant
      -Supports True HD Dolby 7.1 and DTS-HD Master Audio
      -Gold-Plated Connectors: The Micro HDMI to HDMI cable features gold-plated connectors that resist corrosion for signal purity
      Suitable for:
      Mobile telephones / Smartphones / Tablet-PCs / HD-Camcorder / Digital cameras / Media-Center / HDTV devices / Projector / Plasma/TFT-TV / Monitors / DVR / Blu-ray-Player / Home Theatre Systems and more.
      Installation
      Plug-&-play: Ready to use, once each end is connected to a compatible device
      Notes
      -HDMI ports supporting Ethernet are needed for internet sharing.
      -This is not micro USB,Does not work with Samsung Galaxy S3/S4/S5 Or Samsung Tablets with Micro USB Connection.
      Package Contents
      UGREEN Micro HDMI (Type D) to HDMI (Type A) High Speed Cable x 1;
